title: BRIEF-Magellan Midstream Announces Open Season For Potential Expansion Of Western Leg Of Texas Refined Products Pipeline System
text: March 9, 2018 / 2:53 PM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-Magellan Midstream Announces Open Season For Potential Expansion Of Western Leg Of Texas Refined Products Pipeline System Reuters Staff 1 Min Read March 9 (Reuters) - Magellan Midstream Partners Lp: * MAGELLAN MIDSTREAM ANNOUNCES OPEN SEASON FOR POTENTIAL EXPANSION OF WESTERN LEG OF TEXAS REFINED PRODUCTS PIPELINE SYSTEM * MAGELLAN MIDSTREAM - ‍PIPELINE’S CURRENT CAPACITY OF 100,000 BPD COULD INCREASE TO 140,000 BPD FOLLOWING EXPANSION​ * MAGELLAN MIDSTREAM PARTNERS - CUSTOMERS INTERESTED IN OPEN SEASON MUST SUBMIT BINDING COMMITMENTS BY 5:00 P.M. CENTRAL TIME ON MAY 9, 2018​ * MAGELLAN MIDSTREAM - ‍LAUNCHED OPEN SEASON TO ASSESS CUSTOMER INTEREST FOR EXPANSION OF WESTERN LEG OF REFINED PRODUCTS PIPELINE​ SYSTEM Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
